{"type": "article", "id": 30106, "title": "可以摇的沙发", "description": "", "date": "2016-07-25T23:06:23Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 28, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160725214747mE80GoQ5yF7S6dZK.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p><a href=\"http://www.nurseryworks.net/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Nursery Works</a> 的设计师们这次脑洞大开，将两件为人带来舒适感的家具结合在了一起 ，打造了一件兼具沙发和摇椅功能的家具 Ami Rocker。烤漆的钢管支架上有着非常流畅的曲线，依靠底部精心设计的弧度维持着平衡。支架上摆放着柔软的羊毛坐垫和一个摇篮，适合大人和孩子一起坐在上面轻轻摇晃着度过温馨的亲子时光。由于采用了模块化的设计，摇篮也可以换为坐垫，改造成一款双人沙发，有着很强的实用性。这是它的<a href=\"http://www.nurseryworks.net/ami-rocker\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 1250 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160725214806gWbDaI1c5eM9Arxv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666307\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160725214806Vz5aXyUP3d78HfFZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666307\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160725214806ylPG6nY4LA5ZRfSo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666307\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607252148079vGBdUAe0j5psfgE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666307\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}